snippet.title: Moonfrost Livestream Founder Update Series Ep 1
snippet.description:
Welcome to Moonfrost a modern-day life-sim farming RPG set in a beautiful next gen pixel-art world.

Come join us in a brand new Founder Updates Series on Thursday 20th at 12:00 (Noon) UTC, where Gina our Boss Witch & Art Director will be discussing all things Moonfrost including; exposing the secrets of SHARDS. 

You can also head to our channel to find out about our latest news and updates and catch up on any streams missed. 

Website: https://moonfrost.io/
Twitter:  https://moonfrost.io/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/moonfrost
